    "beheira_about_p1": "✝ Egypt.. land of prophets and blessings... and when we came to Kanawa, it became blessed and honored. On their journey through northern Egypt, the Holy Family passed through Wadi El Natrun, that blessed spot that later became a center for Christian monasticism in the world. Since the feet of Christ, the Virgin Mary, and Saint Joseph the Carpenter stepped on the lands of Wadi El Natrun, this region has become a symbol of meditation and worship, where the oldest Christian monasteries were founded.",
