    "sharqia_hero_title": "Sharqia and Delta",
    "sharqia_hero_subtitle": "Follow the first steps of the Holy Family in Egyptian lands through the Delta governorates.",
    "sharqia_about_title": "Sharqia.. A Journey of Faith Through Time",
    "sharqia_about_p1": "Egypt.. land of prophets and blessings ✝ and when we came to Kanawa, it became blessed and honored ... In a journey filled with faith and miracles, the Holy Family settled in the land of Sharqia Governorate, leaving behind lines of light written by destiny in the record of time.",
