    "nature_hero_title": "Nature and Landscapes",
    "nature_hero_subtitle": "Explore the natural beauty that surrounded the Holy Family's journey in Egypt",
    "nature_section_title": "The Beauty of Nature Along the Trail",
    "nature_about_p1": "The Holy Family Trail passes through a variety of stunning landscapes in Egypt, from the fertile Nile Delta to the vast desert and the Nile Valley.",
    "nature_about_p2": "From desert oases to the banks of the Nile, from towering mountains to green plains, the trail offers a unique visual experience that harmonizes with the spiritual experience of the journey.",
